1
00:01:38,327 --> 00:01:41,727
[Goku] We aren't really going to
camp out here, are we?

2
00:01:41,827 --> 00:01:45,327
At least we'll be able to get
out of the rain for a few hours.

3
00:01:45,427 --> 00:01:47,461
[Hakkai] Come on, pull it tight.

4
00:01:47,561 --> 00:01:48,694
[Goku] Damn.

5
00:01:54,861 --> 00:01:58,227
<i>The rain always puts Sanzo</i>
<i>in a bad mood.</i>

6
00:01:58,327 --> 00:02:02,294
<i>I think Hakkai told me why</i>
<i>once, but I've forgotten.</i>

7
00:02:02,394 --> 00:02:05,761
<i>Well, that's got nothing to do</i>
<i>with me anyway.</i>

8
00:02:05,861 --> 00:02:08,594
<i>I don't hate rain that much.</i>

9
00:02:08,694 --> 00:02:11,961
<i>It was my past that always</i>
<i>poured down on me in droves.</i>

10
00:02:13,861 --> 00:02:16,461
<i>I never minded getting</i>
<i>little muddy.</i>

11
00:02:16,561 --> 00:02:20,761
<i>Then again, maybe I convinced</i>
<i>myself the rain could wash</i>
<i>the memories away.</i>

12
00:02:20,861 --> 00:02:23,127
<i>I had been unwilling</i>
<i>to forget.</i>

13
00:02:23,227 --> 00:02:25,161
<i>I use to think like that.</i>

14
00:02:25,261 --> 00:02:28,294
<i>But I'm not the only one here</i>
<i>with scars to heal.</i>

15
00:02:28,394 --> 00:02:31,461
<i>You couldn't severe the bond</i>
<i>between us, even if you tried.</i>

16
00:02:33,261 --> 00:02:37,394
<i>Now that I think about it,</i>
<i>that night three years ago,</i>

17
00:02:37,494 --> 00:02:38,961
<i>it rained like this too.</i>

18
00:02:42,661 --> 00:02:44,527
"The Storm of Fate"

19
00:02:53,727 --> 00:02:56,594
[Gojyo] Aces, four of a kind.

20
00:02:56,694 --> 00:02:59,127
[Girl 1] Yeah!
[Girl 2] You're amazing!

21
00:02:59,227 --> 00:03:02,494
Hey, come on, Gojyo, give me a
break already, will ya?

22
00:03:02,594 --> 00:03:04,861
It's too early to start
complaining, Tongpu.

23
00:03:04,961 --> 00:03:07,494
You still have a few bucks I
haven't won yet.

24
00:03:07,627 --> 00:03:08,594
[Girl 1] That's right.

25
00:03:08,694 --> 00:03:10,261
[Girl 2] The night's
still young.

26
00:03:10,361 --> 00:03:14,194
Tell you what, if I win this
hand here, the next round is
on me, girls.

27
00:03:15,027 --> 00:03:16,594
[All Three] You can do
it, Gojyo!

28
00:03:16,694 --> 00:03:17,861
Wait a minute, is every woman
in this place rooting for
you, Gojyo?

29
00:03:20,194 --> 00:03:22,861
[Girl 4] Of course we are.

30
00:03:22,961 --> 00:03:26,261
You do have the most fantastic
mane of hair.

31
00:03:26,361 --> 00:03:29,261
